{"tid":410194,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我喺乜嘢","createTime":"2017-09-22T16:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T17:07:20.000Z","uid":149162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e286872d422ea2aecb53ec271fd8b8e1a4990e31","tid":410194,"uid":149162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:40:41.000Z","msg":"男朋友同前度分咗手成年<br />\n同我一齊時仲有聯絡<br />\n應承過我會斷聯絡<br />\n因為前度有抑鬱所以五斷住<br />\n後尾呃我話同男仔去旅行<br />\n第一次偷睇手機先知喺同前度去<br />\n嗰時我仲要借錢俾佢去<br />\n我踢爆咗佢<br />\n佢話喺為左我<br />\n想同前度一次過講清楚而去<br />\n<br />\n究竟喺咪玩法<br />\n喺咪我五識玩<br />\n喺咪我太易信人<br />\n點解佢可以咁對我<br />\n我究竟喺啲乜嘢<br />\n已經好攰<br />\n好難忘記一個我信任嘅人去背叛咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1780fb7332e54654924f64a9ef243663265f8852","tid":410194,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:41:42.000Z","msg":"七識玩呀我"},{"pid":"0b92165e43a35e43779b471c32238fca05ad2e92","tid":410194,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73365f401cf1d28d0f3ece147285eb3471896c1b","tid":410194,"uid":98337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:01:01.000Z","msg":"佢係愛你就唔會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845ac9933283967ae0d2e5968de429fa91cb26f8","tid":410194,"uid":149162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係愛你就唔會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以諗緊佢應該係唔愛我先咁做"}]}